<p>Dave and John answer your questions and solve your Mac (and iPad, and iPhone, and&hellip;) problems! Topics today include finding (and removing) that pesky Safari wallpaper, best ways to begin programming on the Mac (and iPhone, and iPad, and&hellip;), best practices for migrating to a new machine, and getting your media directly to your iPad or iPhone, bypassing your Mac. Subscribe today (just $25 for 6 months) and enjoy all this extra Premium content from your two favorite geeks!</p>
